<dl><dd>A.&#160;<link rel="mw-deduplicated-inline-style" href="mw-data:TemplateStyles:r1041539562" /><span class="citation wikicite" id="endnote&#95;AaB"><b><a href="#ref_AaB">^</a></b></span>  Danish club <a href="/wiki/AaB_Fodbold" title="AaB Fodbold">Aalborg</a> played in the <a href="/wiki/1995%E2%80%9396_UEFA_Champions_League" title="1995–96 UEFA Champions League">1995–96 Champions League</a> tournament as a result of the bribing scandal of Dynamo Kyiv, thus they did not qualify through the qualification rounds.</dd></dl>
